The '''Students of Collus''' were a group of student dissenters throughout the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]] at the [[University of Alderaan/Legends|University of Alderaan]]. They named themselves after the [[Alderaan/Legends|Alderaanian]] philosopher [[Collus (philosopher)|Collus]].

